Privacy Policy
Your privacy is important to us, and we want you to understand what we collect, what we don't collect, and what we do with the information that we do collect. This Privacy Policy (the "Policy") applies to the information we collect about visitors to www.tetravpn.com (the "Site") and subscribers to the TetraVPN and related service (the "Services"), which are owned and operated by TetraVPN (contact information below).
Our Terms of Use, including their limitation on liability, apply to the Privacy Policy. You can read them at
here.
